 }}</ref>。这一风暴系统继续向西行进，于8月29日在[[瓜德罗普|瓜德罗普]]以东超过320公里外洋面发展成热带低气压<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140409092642/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2013-040114.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2013-040114.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2014-04-01 | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | archivedate = 2014-04-09}}</ref>。由于附近一个[[反气旋|反气旋]]提供了有利于系统发展的[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]，低气压也在朝小安的列斯群岛移动的过程中逐渐增强<ref name="MWR">{{cite journal
