 | accessdate = March 30, 2010
 | url = http://journals.ametsoc.org/doi/pdf/10.1175/1520-0493%281975%29103%3C0285%3AAHSO%3E2.0.CO%3B2
 | pages = 289-290
 | format = PDF
 | doi = 10.1175/1520-0493(1975)103<0285:AHSO>2.0.CO;2
 | issn = 1520-0493
 | bibcode = 1975MWRv..103..285H}}</ref>。8月30日，系统在[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]以南海域达到热带风暴强度<ref name="HURDAT" />，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]因此将其命名为“卡门”（{{lang|en|Carmen}}）<ref>{{cite web | author = Neil Frank | title = Tropical Storm Carmen Special Advisory Number 1 | date = 1974-08-30 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | format = JPG | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | archivedate = 2014-05-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140529015947/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0188-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/public/pub302300z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0188-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/public/pub302300z.jpg}}</ref>。风暴起初朝[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]接近，令其无法得到进一步强化<ref>{{cite web | author = John R. Hope | title = Tropical Cyclone Discussion Tropical Storm Carmen | date = 1974-08-31 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | archivedate = 2014-05-29 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140529020304/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0188-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/tropdisc/tcd310300z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0188-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/tropdisc/tcd310300z.jpg}}</ref>，但到了8月31日却又已达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的一级飓风强度<ref name="HURDAT" />。卡门经过[[牙买加|牙买加]]以南海域后，其中还短暂出现了[[风眼|眼状特征]]<ref>{{cite web | author = | title = Tropical Cyclone Discussion Tropical Storm Carmen | date = 1974-08-31 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140529020528/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0188-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/tropdisc/tcd311500z.jpg | archivedate = 2014-05-29 | format = JPG | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0188-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/tropdisc/tcd311500z.jpg}}</ref>。

9月1日，飓风开始在[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]的温暖海域上空[[爆发性增强|爆发性增强]]，到[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]下午18点已达到四级飓风强度<ref name="HURDAT" />。卡門继续向西行进，于当晚从[[天鹅群岛|天鹅群岛]]以北洋面经过<ref name="MWR" />。9月2日清晨，卫星图像显示飓风中出现了[[眼墙置换|双层风眼墙]]<ref>{{cite web | author = John R. Hope | title = Tropical Cyclone Discussion Hurricane Carmen | date = 1974-09-02 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0188-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/tropdisc/tcd020300z.jpg | format = JPG | archivedate = 2014-05-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140529021655/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0188-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/tropdisc/tcd020300z.jpg}}</ref>。随着风暴开始由西向北移动，其前进速度逐渐放缓<ref>{{cite web | author = Joseph M. Pelissier | title = Tropical Cyclone Discussion Hurricane Carmen | date = 1974-09-02 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | format = JPG | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024060513/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0188-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/tropdisc/tcd020900z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0188-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/tropdisc/tcd020900z.jpg}}</ref>并达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时240公里，中心[[气压|气压]]928[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，27.4[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度<ref name="HURDAT" />。大气中的转向气流变得越来越弱，卡门的飘移速度也因此放缓<ref>{{cite web | author = Neil Frank | title = Tropical Cyclone Discussion Hurricane Carmen | date = 1974-09-02 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | format = JPG | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024060426/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0188-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/tropdisc/tcd022100z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0188-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/tropdisc/tcd022100z.jpg}}</ref>。9月2日晚，飓风在尤卡坦半岛登陆，其北面没有直接袭击[[伯利兹市|伯利兹市]]。风暴中心在[[金塔纳罗奥州|金塔纳罗奥州]][[切图马尔|切图马尔]]以北仅数英里外经过<ref name="HURDAT" />。

气旋向内陆飘移，于9月3日减弱成热带风暴<ref name="HURDAT" />。过了约一天后，卡门进入墨西哥湾并且几乎一度停止前进，然后转向北上，于9月5日再次增强到飓风标准<ref name="HURDAT" />。风暴继续增强并加速北上，逼近[[美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区|美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区]]<ref name="MWR" />，前进速度达到每小时19公里，并在{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}9月7日凌晨0点达到三级强度，再次成为大型飓风<ref name="HURDAT" />。卡丽在路易斯安那州以南洋面达到第二波强度高峰，不过其风速虽与之前的最高强度相同，但气压却要略高。飓风在登陆前有所减弱并向西转向，最终袭击的是路易斯安那州中南部。卡丽登岸后迅速减弱，于9月9日晚退化成热带低气压。低气压向西行进，之后不久就在德克萨斯州东部上空消散<ref name="HURDAT" />。

== 防灾措施 ==
[[File:Hurricane_Carmen_near_United_States_Landfall_1974.jpg|thumb]]，即将[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]的飓风卡门。]]
根据美国媒体的报道，尤卡坦半岛起初面对这场逼近飓风的反应较为平静。墨西哥官方于9月2日发布紧急警报，但没有建议居民撤离，反倒是美国的[[气象学|气象专家]]敦促生活在沿海地区的居民立即采取行动转移到内陆<ref name="TVA1">{{cite news | author = Associated Press | work = The Victoria Advocate | date = 1974-09-02 | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | title = Hurricane Grows, Yucatan Target of Carmen | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=861&dat=19740902&id=ZQtaAAAAIBAJ&sjid=ZUsNAAAAIBAJ&pg=6606,241459}}</ref>。由于担心会出现重大生命和财产损失，[[国际红十字与红新月运动|红十字会]]开始在伯利兹针对即将到来的飓风做准备<ref name="TVA1" />。次日，[[墨西哥陆军|墨西哥陆军]]赶到5座城市设立紧急行动中心和避难所，还有移动通讯组和救援队做好在风暴过境后进行部署的准备<ref name="BCT1">{{cite news | author = United Press International | work = Beaver Country Times | date = 1974-09-03 | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | title = Carmen Sweeps Across Yucatan | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=A-EtAAAAIBAJ&sjid=yNoFAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane%20carmen%20yucatan&pg=2370%2C208095}}</ref>。切图马尔市内及周边的多达近3.5万居民疏散到了地势更高的地方<ref name="SHT1">{{cite news | author = United Press International | work = Sarasota Herald-Tribune | date = 1974-09-03 | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | title = Carmen Smashes Across Yucatan (Part One) | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=CfwjAAAAIBAJ&sjid=62YEAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane%20carmen%20yucatan&pg=6386%2C1154179}}</ref>。

飓风起初对新奥尔良构成威胁，但在登陆前转向朝西，该市因此没有受到严重破坏<ref name="MWR" />。气象部门一度预测卡丽会突然向东转向朝[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]逼近，这与实际情况正好相反。如果气旋继续北上经过[[庞恰特雷恩湖|庞恰特雷恩湖]]上空，低洼地区可能遭受“灾难性”的洪水袭击<ref name="LA preps">{{cite news | author = Associated Press | title = Hurricane Carmen batters Louisiana | date = 1974-09-08 | publisher = ''The Southeast Missourian'' | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=gtEfAAAAIBAJ&sjid=2dgEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1178,717871}}</ref>。[[美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区|墨西哥湾沿岸]]有超过10万居民在飓风来袭前撤离，其中又以路易斯安那州和[[密西西比州|密西西比州]]为主<ref>{{cite news | author =  | title = Carmen lashes coast | date = 1974-09-08 | publisher = ''The Chicago Tribune'' | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/chicagotribune/access/607737012.html?dids=607737012:607737012&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Sep+08%2C+1974&author=&pub=Chicago+Tribune&desc=Carmen+lashes+coast&pqatl=google | archive-date = 2012-10-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121026123927/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/chicagotribune/access/607737012.html?dids=607737012:607737012&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Sep+08,+1974&author=&pub=Chicago+Tribune&desc=Carmen+lashes+coast&pqatl=google | dead-url = no }}</ref>，造成[[高速公路|高速公路]]严重挤塞<ref name="LA preps" />。据红十字会官员透露，整个新奥尔良地区有约6万人寻求庇护设施<ref>{{cite news | author = Associated Press | title = Carmen sputters | date = 1974-09-09 | publisher = ''The Park City Daily News'' | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=eCQqAAAAIBAJ&sjid=qkYEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6606,1394818}}</ref>。

气象部门向海岸沿线发布了[[热带气旋警告|飓风警告]]，[[海岸巡防队|海岸巡防队]]人员在[[格兰德艾尔_(路易斯安那州)|格兰德艾尔]]挨家挨户上门敦促居民撤离该地区，并且从这里一直到佛罗里达州西南部沿海的小型船只都收到建议留在海岸附近，避免在风大浪急的情况下出海<ref>{{cite news | author = Associated Press | title = Hurricane Carmen Rages North | date = 1974-09-07 | publisher = ''The Ottawa Citizen'' | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=zb0yAAAAIBAJ&sjid=7-wFAAAAIBAJ&pg=1010,1806048}}</ref>。海上石油平台的工作人员予以撤离<ref>{{cite news | author = Associated Press | title = Weather Service Warns Hurricane Carmen Will Strike Gulf Coast Area | date = 1974-09-04 | publisher = ''The Times-News'' | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ZhsaAAAAIBAJ&sjid=eCQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=2522,450488}}</ref>。密西西比州沿海地区的许多公民对五年前毁灭性的[[飓风卡米尔|飓风卡米尔]]仍然记忆犹新，因此迅速离开了自己的家园<ref>{{cite news | author = Associated Press | title = Gulf Residents Recall Camille | date = 1974-09-08 | publisher = ''The Herald-Journal'' | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ii8sAAAAIBAJ&sjid=_ssEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7315,1357318 | accessdate = 2014-05-29}}</ref>。

== 影响 ==
气旋还处于热带低气压和热带风暴阶段时给[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]和北部小安的列斯群岛带去了中等程度降水，[[卡耶伊|卡耶伊]]的贾乔米奥托（{{lang|en|Jajome Alto}}）降雨量最高，达到150毫米<ref name="HPC">{{cite web | author = David Roth | title = Hurricane Carmen – August 29 – September 11, 1974 | date = | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/carmen1974.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921215720/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/carmen1974.html | archivedate = 2013-09-21}}</ref>。风暴在波多黎各催生出一场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]并引起山洪爆发，共计造成了超过200万美元（1974年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|2000000|1974}}}}美元）的损失<ref name="MWR" />。多个受影响岛屿的风速接近[[蒲福风级|烈风强度]]<ref>{{cite news | author = Associated Press | title = New storm builds, Becky heads north | date = 1974-08-30 | publisher = ''The Bangor Daily News'' | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=FgM0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=KyMIAAAAIBAJ&pg=3426,4985064&dq=puerto+rico+storm+flood&hl=en | archive-date = 2019-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190304235834/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=FgM0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=KyMIAAAAIBAJ&pg=3426,4985064&dq=puerto+rico+storm+flood&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。伊斯帕尼奥拉岛在风暴途经西部近海期间普降暴雨<ref>{{cite news | author = Associated Press | title = Hurricane No. 2 | date = 1974-09-01 | publisher = ''La Nación'' | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=jqUeAAAAIBAJ&sjid=fc8EAAAAIBAJ&pg=3324,11577163&dq=tropical-storm-carmen+haiti&hl=en | archive-date = 2019-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190304235834/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=jqUeAAAAIBAJ&sjid=fc8EAAAAIBAJ&pg=3324,11577163&dq=tropical-storm-carmen+haiti&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>，牙买加有3人因卡门溺毙<ref>{{cite news | author = Associated Press | title = Storm May Regain Hurricane Strength | date = 1974-09-04 | publisher = ''The Argus-Press'' | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=nG0iAAAAIBAJ&sjid=sawFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4436,163167&dq=tropical+storm+carmen+jamaica&hl=en | archive-date = 2019-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190304235834/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=nG0iAAAAIBAJ&sjid=sawFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4436,163167&dq=tropical+storm+carmen+jamaica&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>，该岛和[[古巴|古巴]]都经报道受到狂风暴雨的冲击<ref>{{cite news | author = Associated Press | title = Carmen Roars Toward Yucatan | date = 1974-09-01 | publisher = ''The Victoria Advocate'' | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=861&dat=19740901&id=ZAtaAAAAIBAJ&sjid=ZUsNAAAAIBAJ&pg=6854,11144}}</ref>。飓风途经期间还破坏了牙买加北岸的[[珊瑚礁|珊瑚礁]]<ref>{{cite web | author = J.S. Levinton | title = Coral Reefs: limiting factors, morphology, and nutrition of corals | publisher = Prentice-Hall | accessdate = 2012-09-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120921015201/http://www.geology.iupui.edu/academics/classes/g130/reefs/ME_20.htm | url = http://www.geology.iupui.edu/Academics/CLASSES/G130/reefs/ME_20.htm | archivedate = 2012-09-21 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

风暴过后，其名称予以退役，永远不会再在北大西洋热带气旋命名时使用<ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Hurricane Center | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | title = Retired Hurricane Names Since 1954 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutnames_history.shtml#retired | archivedate = 2014-02-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140228015223/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutnames_history.shtml#retired | deadurl = no}}</ref>。不过由于1979年时命名机制出现调整，这个名字并没有由任何一个特定名称取代<ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Hurricane Center | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140228015223/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutnames_history.shtml | title = Worldwide Tropical Cyclone Names: History | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutnames_history.shtml | archivedate = 2014-02-28 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

=== 尤卡坦半岛 ===
[[File:Hurricane_Carmen.JPG|thumb]]
虽然卡门登陆时属强劲的四级飓风，但由于直接吹袭地区人烟稀少，因此造成的损失远小于预期。但风暴产生的连场暴雨还是令大片区域的耕地被淹，水稻作物受损严重，捕鱼业也遭受了重大损失。飓风路途上那些受灾最严重地区的通讯也相应中断，早期的报道表明至少有5人受伤<ref name="BCT1" />。几天后，墨西哥官方确认有三人直接因风暴丧生，切图马尔市“满目疮痍”，数以百计的居民流离失所<ref>{{cite news | author = Associated Press | work = Bangor Daily News | date = 1974-09-06 | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | title = Hurricane watch out along Gulf | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=4HEzAAAAIBAJ&sjid=lyMIAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane%20carmen%20yucatan&pg=535%2C1669889}}</ref>。该市有超过5000人因这场风暴失去了自己的财产。当地官员估计仅切图马尔的经济损失就达到800万美元（1974年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|8000000|1974}}}}美元）<ref name="TMG1">{{cite news | author = United Press International | work = The Montreal Gazette | date = 1974-09-04 | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | title = Hurricane stalls, getting weaker | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=BQwyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=u6EFAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane%20carmen%20yucatan%20damage&pg=2748%2C350502}}</ref>。飓风卡门共计在尤卡坦半岛夺走了4条人命，造成的破坏价值1000万美元（1974年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|10000000|1974}}}}美元）<ref>{{cite news | author = United Press International | work = Beaver Country Times | date = 1974-09-06 | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | title = Hurricane Gathers Strength In Gulf | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=BuEtAAAAIBAJ&sjid=yNoFAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane%20carmen%20yucatan%20damage&pg=4255%2C1401653}}</ref>。

卡门过境后，伯利兹有约2590平方公里区域与外界失去联系，对此政府担心出现了极其严重的灾情，并在风暴过后次日就从伯利兹市派出侦察特遣部队，对任何因风暴受困的居民提供协助<ref name="SHT2">{{cite news | author = United Press International | work = Sarasota Herald-Tribune | date = 1974-09-03 | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | title = Carmen Smashes Across Yucatan (Part Two) | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=CfwjAAAAIBAJ&sjid=62YEAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane%20carmen%20yucatan&pg=1798%2C1169512}}</ref>。伯利兹近海有一人被卡门产生的涌浪冲下船后遇难，另外还有三位渔民因类似情况失踪。沿海地区数以千计的居民转移到内陆躲避风暴袭击，报道显示该国也遭受了严重的农作物损失<ref>{{cite news | author = United Press International | work = The Bryan Times | date = 1974-09-04 | title = Carmen stalls in Gulf, 2 other storms develop}}</ref>。

=== 美国 ===
卡门沿途普遍降中雨，降雨量最大的区域在风暴中心以东的[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]]南部和[[佛罗里达州狭长地带|佛罗里达州狭长地带]]北部，[[阿特莫尔_(阿拉巴马州)|阿特莫尔]]降雨量达到最高的330毫米<ref name="HPC" />。阵风时速达到138公里，沿岸潮汐比正常水位高1.8米<ref name="MWR" />。路易斯安那州西北部上空的风速范围在每小时64到72公里之间，吹倒许多树木<ref>{{cite web | author = National Weather Service Shreveport | title = Preliminary Post Storm Report: Hurricane Carmen | date = 1974-09-09 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024042934/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0189-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/preloc/shv091730z.jpg | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0189-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/preloc/shv091730z.jpg}}</ref>。新奥尔良阵风时速达到116公里，幸好造成的破坏不大<ref>{{cite web | author = National Weather Service New Orleans | title = Preliminary Storm Report: Hurricane Carmen | date = 1974-09-09 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | format = JPG | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024042941/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0189-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/preloc/msy092027z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0189-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/preloc/msy092027z.jpg}}</ref>。[[巴吞鲁日_(路易斯安那州)|巴吞鲁日]]受到的影响仅限于少量树木倒塌和一些散落的瓦砾<ref>{{cite web | author = National Weather Service Baton Rouge | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Carmen | date = 1974-09-09 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | format = JPG | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024042950/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0189-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/preloc/btr091300z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0189-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/preloc/btr091300z.jpg}}</ref>。

卡门登陸区域荒无人烟，造成的破坏远低於预期<ref>{{cite news | author = Associated Press | title = Hurricane Carmen dies out | date = 1974-09-09 | publisher = ''The Rome News-Tribune'' | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=X7EFAAAAIBAJ&sjid=LjMDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3263,1184100}}</ref>。不过墨西哥湾的潮汐洪水和近海河湖的洪灾严重，淡水洪灾相对较轻。风暴产生的洪水淹没了路易安那州96万3400公顷陆地，其中[[泰勒博恩堂区_(路易斯安那州)|泰勒博恩堂区]]有30万零400公顷，[[普拉克明堂区_(路易斯安那州)|普拉克明堂区]]有24万公顷<ref name="phase">{{cite report | author = | title = Inventory and Assessment of Existing Economic and Resource Conditions | date = 1997-07-31 | publisher = Louisiana Department of Natural Resources}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | publisher = United States Corps of Engineers | date = 2004-12-14 | accessdate = 2013-02-15 | title = Final Programmatic Environmental Impact Statement: Mississippi River & Tributaries-Morganza, Louisiana To The Gulf Of Mexico Hurricane Protection | archivedate = 2013-02-15 | format = DOC | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130215140145/http://www.mvn.usace.army.mil/pd/projectslist/ProjectData/118926/reports/FinalPEISSummary.doc | url = http://www.mvn.usace.army.mil/pd/projectslist/ProjectData/118926/reports/FinalPEISSummary.doc}}</ref>。
[[File:Carmen_1974_rainfall.png|left]]的降雨量分布，黄色线条，标有“{{lang|en|Track}}”字样的是风暴路径，左下部有图例，表明不同颜色部分的降雨量范围，右下部表明降雨量最高的是阿拉巴马州阿特莫尔，达13.2英寸（330毫米）。左上角标出飓风名称及持续时间（1974年9月6至11日），还标出了数据来源（1373处测量点）。]]

受这场风暴影响最严重的是路易斯安那州的糖类作物，估计有16个堂区的12.5万公顷甘蔗受到破坏，报道称其中20%被毁<ref>{{cite news | author = United Press International | title = Hurricane Carmen hurts sugar crop | date = 1974-09-09 | publisher = ''The Lodi News-Sentinel'' | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=95gzAAAAIBAJ&sjid=bzIHAAAAIBAJ&pg=6099,558955}}</ref>。当时的[[路易斯安那州州长列表|州长]][[埃德温·爱德华兹|埃德温·爱德华兹]]（{{lang|en|Edwin Edwards}}）在视察灾区后估计仅农作物损失就达到400万美元（1974年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|4000000|1974}}}}美元）<ref name="Beaver">{{cite news | author = United Press International | title = Carmen Leaves Her Mark | date = 1974-09-09 | publisher = ''The Beaver Country Times'' | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=COEtAAAAIBAJ&sjid=yNoFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2282,1792253}}</ref>，另据之后的一项研究估计，这场飓风总计造成的农业损失约为7400万美元（1974年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|74000000|1974}}}}美元）<ref name="phase" />。甘蔗作物是美国食糖供应链中至关重要的原料，这让损失变得更为严重<ref name="Beaver" />，糖类[[期货|期货]]也在风暴过后出现大幅上涨<ref>{{cite news | author = Elizabeth M. Fowler | title = Sugar Prices Soar Daily Limit On Effect of Hurricane Carmen; Cotton Declines November Delivery Up Cash Prices Open Interest | date = 1974-09-10 | publisher = The New York Times Company | work = The New York Times | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | archivedate = 2012-11-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121103040530/http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F10B17F93A551A7493C2A81782D85F408785F9 | url = http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F10B17F93A551A7493C2A81782D85F408785F9}}</ref>。其它受到破坏的农作物还包括大豆、水稻和棉花<ref name="phase" />。

海岸沿线的潮汐对沿海沼泽及河流湖泊的盐度平衡产生影响。突然进入的海水烧毁了植物，鱼、虾、牡蛎也受到飓风卡门的生态影响。一些陆上野生动物因洪水淹死。路易斯安那州的多所公园受到洪水或强风的破坏。[[格兰德艾尔_(路易斯安那州)|格兰德艾尔]]共计遭受了11.46万美元（1974年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|114600|1974}}}}美元）的损失。[[石油|石油]]和[[天然气|天然气]]产业也受到影响，损失估计有2470万美元（1974年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|24700000|1974}}}}美元），其中大部分是因设备和海上设施损坏。多个地点因风暴来袭暂停原油开采24或48小时，石油产量因此减少了140万桶<ref name="phase" />。有超过6万户电气合作社用户失去电力供应<ref>{{cite web | author = | title = History | date = | publisher = Dixie Electric Membership Corporation | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140106042011/http://www.demco.org/about-us/history | archivedate = 2014-01-06 | url = http://www.demco.org/about-us/history}}</ref>。

飓风还导致路易斯安那州两人丧生，其中一位是公用事业维修工人，他在试图修复受狂风破坏的供电线路时触电身亡<ref name="Beaver" />，另一位则是在风暴引起的交通事故中丧生的司机<ref>{{cite news | author = Associated Press | title = Hurricane Carmen Leaves Two Dead; Ravages Crops | date = 1974-09-10 | publisher = ''The Virgin Islands Daily News'' | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=KzETAAAAIBAJ&sjid=BK4DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6472,909464}}</ref>。该州总计受到的财产损失约在1.5亿美元（1974年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|150000000|1974}}}}美元）左右<ref name="MWR" />。卡门还共计催生了四场龙卷风<ref>{{cite web | author = Tom Grazulis and Bill McCaul | title = List of Known Tropical Cyclones Which Have Spawned Tornadoes | date = | publisher = Tornado Project | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | url = http://www.tornadoproject.com/alltorns/allhurricanes.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131212032742/http://www.tornadoproject.com/alltorns/allhurricanes.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-12-12}}</ref>，其中一个在密西西比州的[[兰金县_(密西西比州)|兰金县]][[县城|县城]][[布兰登_(密西西比州)|布兰登]]（{{lang|en|Brandon}}）着陆，摧毁了一座谷仓，还造成了其它破坏<ref>{{cite web | author = National Weather Service Jackson | title = Preliminary Post Storm Report: Hurricane Carmen | date = 1974-09-09 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | format = JPG | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024042957/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0189-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/preloc/jan091600z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0189-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/preloc/jan091600z.jpg}}</ref>。另一场龙卷风在路易斯安那州的[[卡普兰_(路易斯安那州)|卡普兰]]引起两人受伤<ref>{{cite web | author = National Weather Service Lake Charles | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Carmen | date = 1974-09-08 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024043022/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0189-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/preloc/lch081945z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0189-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/preloc/lch081945z.jpg}}</ref>。密西西比州受这场风暴的影响很小，主要局限在强降水过程中出现的轻微交通意外<ref>{{cite web | author = National Weather Service Jackson | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Carmen | date = 1974-09-11 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-29 | format = JPG | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024043030/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0189-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/preloc/jan111315z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0189-jpg/1974/atlantic/carmen/preloc/jan111315z.jpg}}</ref>。风暴给大范围地区带去降雨，向东直至佛罗里达州和[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]，向西直至[[俄克拉何马州|俄克拉何马州]]和德克萨斯州都出现了小到中雨<ref name="HPC" />。

